::Dragoon::
       His eyes got big as he saw Hot Rod start to fire.  He dropped straight 
down with one shot hitting each wing with no major damage.  The other two 
shots soared over head toward Lucenite while his two blasts flew past at Hot 
Rod.  "Whoa.  I'm outa here."  He takes off straight away from them and 
quickly drops out of sight into the forest.

--part1_5b.1f4cbbc6.294196eb_boundary
